<view class="page">
  <view class="page-shell" style="padding-top: {{statusBarHeight + 10}}px;">
    <view class="floating-label">16 今日榜单 / 榜单详情</view>

    <view class="hero-card">
      <view class="hero-eyebrow">TODAY RANKING</view>
      <view class="hero-title">追踪今天最值得跟进的热点、低粉爆款和涨粉方向</view>
      <view class="hero-desc">从实时热度、互动表现和转化潜力三个维度，帮助你决定今天先拆哪一类内容。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="stat-grid">
      <view class="stat-card">
        <view class="stat-value">24h</view>
        <view class="stat-label">热度刷新</view>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-card">
        <view class="stat-value">03</view>
        <view class="stat-label">榜单分类</view>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-card">
        <view class="stat-value">实时</view>
        <view class="stat-label">更新状态</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-card">
      <view class="section-head">
        <view class="section-title">榜单筛选</view>
        <view class="section-hint">按热度切换</view>
      </view>
      <view class="filter-row">
        <view class="filter-pill filter-pill-active">热点榜</view>
        <view class="filter-pill">低粉爆款</view>
        <view class="filter-pill">高涨粉榜</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-card">
      <view class="section-head">
        <view class="section-title">热点榜单 TOP 5</view>
        <view class="section-hint">右侧滑动查看更多</view>
      </view>
      <view class="ranking-list">
        <view class="ranking-item" wx:for="{{rankingRows}}" wx:key="index">
          <view class="row-index {{item.toneClass}}">{{item.index}}</view>
          <view class="row-copy">
            <view class="row-title">{{item.title}}</view>
            <view class="row-meta">{{item.meta}}</view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-card section-card-soft">
      <view class="section-head">
        <view class="section-title">榜单使用建议</view>
        <view class="section-hint">先判断，再拆解</view>
      </view>
      <view class="section-body">建议先看热度最高的 1 条，再对比低粉爆款与高涨粉方向。这样能更快判断今天该先做趋势跟进、拆解模仿，还是直接输出自己的观点内容。</view>
    </view>

    <view class="footer-row">
      <view class="footer-btn footer-btn-secondary" bindtap="goBack">返回首页</view>
      <view class="footer-btn footer-btn-primary">查看完整榜单</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
